OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FQuickly
OL,6,Fclouding over this evening, with
OL,7,Foutbreaks of rain developing after
OL,8,Fnightfall. Staying wet overnight, with
OL,9,Fsome heavier bursts possible, most
OL,10,Flikely over high ground. Southwesterly
OL,11,Fwinds increasing with strongest speeds
OL,12,Falong exposed coasts and high ground.
OL,13,
OL,14,CFriday:FA blustery day, with showery
OL,15,Foutbreaks of rain, these could be
OL,16,Fheavy at times, easing later. A few
OL,17,Fbright or sunny spells possible,
OL,18,Fmainly during the late afternoon.
OL,19,FFeeling mild.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
